data.description: Home is A/C-contingent on the sale of the buyers home, still welcoming showings and offers.  Welcome to 848 Schoolhouse Lane, located in Woodcrest. With this home comes the appeal of living in a development without an HOA. You will find this 4 bedroom 2.5 bath home the combination of space, comfort and convienience. With a 2-car garage, it provides ample parking and storage. First floor laundry room, 1/2 bath & new flooring in the kitchen along with other updates throughout.  The family room includes a brick fire-place and built-in shelving/cabinets. The sliding glass doors from the family room take you into an enclosed porch with peaceful backyard views. The foyer brings you to a small set of stairs that enter you into the living room with plenty of natural sunlight. Another small stair case brings you from the living room to the 4 bedrooms and 2 full baths. This property is conveniently located near Dover schools, shopping and dining.  Book your showing & come check out this home!
